@startuml
title pyArchimate Deployment Diagram

node DeveloperWorkstation {
  node "Python 3.12+ runtime" as PythonRuntime
  artifact "pyArchimate CLI / automation" as CLI
  artifact "pyArchimate library" as Library
}
node CIRunner {
  node "CI Python runtime" as PyCI
  artifact "pyArchimate CLI" as CLI_CI
  artifact "pyArchimate library" as Library_CI
}
node Filesystem {
  artifact "Archi/Archimate/ARIS sources" as Sources
  artifact "Archimate/Archi/CSV exports" as Exports
}
node Logging {
  artifact "pyArchimate logs" as Logs
}
node Dependencies {
  artifact "lxml / oyaml / stdlib helpers" as Deps
}
actor "Designer" as Designer
actor "Automation / CI" as Automation

Designer --> CLI : runs scripts
Automation --> CLI_CI : triggers CI automation
CLI --> Library : imports core API
CLI_CI --> Library_CI : imports core API
Library --> Deps : leverages helpers
Library_CI --> Deps
Library --> Sources : reads Archi/Archimate/ARIS sources
Library_CI --> Sources
Library --> Logs : emits warnings/errors
Library_CI --> Logs
Library --> Exports : writes Archimate / Archi / CSV
Library_CI --> Exports
@enduml
